**Investigate this network connection immediately.** Determine the legitimacy of the connection. If suspicious, block the destination IP/port, isolate the affected system, and conduct a full malware analysis. This activity might be an indicator of compromise (IOC) for malware using `IMEWDBLD.exe` as a proxy.
